&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Neora Valley National Park&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is situated in the Kalimpong district,&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;West Bengal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
